    "body" : "<p>Use its <code>name()</code> method:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public class Main {\n    public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {\n        System.out.println(Strings.ONE.name());\n    }\n}\n\nenum Strings {\n    ONE, TWO, THREE\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>yields <code>ONE</code>.</p>\n"
