  "title" : "Best way to create enum of strings?",
  "body" : "<p>What is the best way to have a <code>enum</code> type represent a set of strings?</p>\n\n<p>I tried this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>enum Strings{\n   STRING_ONE(\"ONE\"), STRING_TWO(\"TWO\")\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>How can I then use them as <code>Strings</code>?</p>\n"
}